-- MOVES-Lazard Middle Market appoints two managing directors
-- 
-- Mon Sep 15, 2014 12:50PM EDT
-- None



Sept 15 (Reuters) - Financial adviser Lazard Middle Market, a unit of Lazard Ltd <LAZ.N>, appointed two managing directors as it expands its coverage in the industrial and energy specialty sectors.

James Conniff, to be based in Chicago, previously worked at Robert W. Baird & Co as a managing director in the industrials practice.